data.description: Discover sophistication in this 2020-constructed home, poised in a coveted neighborhood free from HOA. Spanning across three bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, this residence merges time-honored aesthetics with present-day opulence. Within its walls, you'll find lustrous hardwood floors and superior finishes, notably in the refined kitchen outfitted with quartz countertops and the owner's retreat, which boasts a deep soaking tub. The living area's ambiance is enriched by a gas fireplace, while efficiency is addressed with a tankless water heater. The exterior features a private backyard sanctuary with pristine landscaping. Situated within the esteemed Williamson County School district, with proximity to I-40W and the charming Downtown Franklin, this home stands as a testament to stylish and comfortable living. Additionally, the sale includes all mounted TV's!   Preferred Lender offering buyer incentives | Free Appraisal and 2-1 Rate Buydown - Lending Hand Mortgage.
